column1: #Text=So , have you watched [ Avengers ] Infinity War ?
#Text=Do you think Thanos did nothing wrong ?
#Text=I feel , umm , I feel there is a little bit of wrong in both sides . [ Laughs again ] .
#Text=I feel like there 're , there 's a little bit of , um ... there should be more compassion from each side . [ Laughs ]
#Text=So , if you could resurrect one character , one superhero which died in the movie , because of Thanos , whom would you resurrect ?
#Text=Whom would you bring back to life ?
#Text=What would you have done if you were not into comics ?
#Text=I ca n't see myself doing anything else .
#Text=I would be a painter , if I did n't do comics I would be a painter .
#Text=I would probably be into some sort of sports , because I 'm really active , physically , so . [ Laughs ]
#Text=Well , are you looking forward to watching the Spider-Verse movie ?
#Text=But Gwenpool , oh I am sorry , Spider-Girl is coming .
#Text=But I am not a big fan of the Spider-Verse , but I mean , it 's cool .
#Text=let 's say , when he punches someone , there 's " POW ! " written in the bubbles .
#Text=I have n't seen the trailer so .
#Text=One last thing : if you had a message for your younger self , what it probably would be ?
#Text=Do you mind if I take a photo ?
